{
  "stem": "10859.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We couldn't, of course, sit down.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we kept inside the little string to keep this little door, you know, closed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And it didn't take long, maybe about 10 minutes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I hear the crying and screaming when they start taking all the people from the house-- my-- my mother, my sister, and all the children.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It was just unbearable.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It was just unbelievable.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "We-- we said to each other, should we jump out and get out toward?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, one thing I can tell you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If I would have been in the partisans before, we would have jumped out from the chimney and take that-- there was only one man there, a policemen.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we would kill him over there, just with our hand.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We would grab him by his neck.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then we would've gotten the rifle with us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I didn't know even, at that time, how to use a rifle.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "From my religious yeshiva, I didn't know-- I didn't learn how to use a rifle.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that's the way it happened.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They took out all the people from there while we were standing over there and crying.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- and we were staying there in the chimney until it got dark, from 10:00 in the morning.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In summer, the days are long-- probably till 9 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's about-- probably about 12 hours.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And by that time, they managed to take out all the people except maybe some was hiding or ran away, you know, like we just happened-- a few, maybe.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they killed them all out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "How did we know?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was one who ran away from there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And one lifted up the shovel and killed a German right on the spot.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
